> django-admin startproject smallprojects
> python3 manage.py runserver
> python3 manage.py migrate
> python3 manage.py createsuperuser
> python3 manage.py runserver
> python3 manage.py startapp userLogin
> python3 manage.py makemigrations
> python3 manage.py migrate
> python -m django --version

Install crispy-forms
> pip3 install django-crispy-forms
For connecting to MongoDb we need to install
> pip3 install djongo
In Setting.py file change the DATABASES to 

DATABASES = {
    'default': {
        'ENGINE': 'djongo',
        'NAME': 'projects',
    }
}

#using ImageFields in project we need to install Pillow
> pip3 install Pillow	





